<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RISE BW ICON</title>
<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #ffffff;
}
header {
    background: #111;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #00ffcc;
}
nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #000;
    padding: 10px;
}
nav a {
    color: white;
    margin: 0 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}
nav a:hover {
    color: #00ffcc;
}
.hero {
    padding: 100px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #000, #111);
}
.hero h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
}
.btn {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    margin: 10px;
    background: #00ffcc;
    border: none;
    color: black;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
.cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
}
.card {
    background: #111;
    margin: 15px;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 250px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}
footer {
    background: #000;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
input, textarea {
    width: 80%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>RISE BW ICON</h1>
<p>Rebuilding Identity. Empowering Talent. Elevating Botswana.</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#icons">ICON System</a>
<a href="#nominate">Nominate</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Discover Botswana’s True Icons</h2>
<p>A platform to empower, elevate and showcase talent.</p>
<button class="btn">Nominate an ICON</button>
<button class="btn">Join Movement</button>
</section>

<section id="about" class="section">
<h2>About</h2>
<p>RISE BW ICON is a national empowerment initiative focused on identifying and elevating individuals who demonstrate excellence, impact, and authenticity.</p>
</section>

<section id="icons" class="section">
<h2>ICON Categories</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card">Music & Arts</div>
<div class="card">Business</div>
<div class="card">Sports</div>
<div class="card">Culture</div>
<div class="card">Leadership</div>
<div class="card">Technology</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="nominate" class="section">
<h2>Nominate an ICON</h2>
<form>
<input type="text" placeholder="Full Name"><br>
<input type="text" placeholder="Category"><br>
<input type="text" placeholder="Location"><br>
<textarea placeholder="Describe Impact"></textarea><br>
<button class="btn">Submit</button>
</form>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<p>To discover, develop, and showcase individuals who inspire transformation and economic growth.</p>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="section">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: info@risebwicon.com</p>
<p>Phone: +267 XXX XXX</p>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 RISE BW ICON | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
